        "name": null,
        "stories": 2,
        "text": "Welcome to this beautifully renovated single-family bungalow that perfectly blends classic charm with modern updates. This inviting home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 1-1/2 bathrooms, thoughtfully updated for comfortable everyday living. Come inside to discover natural hardwood floors and rich original woodwork that add warmth and character throughout the home, complemented by energy-efficient LED lighting throughout. The fully updated kitchen showcases brand-new appliances and modern waterfall-inspired fixtures, creating a sleek and stylish space for cooking and entertaining. One bathroom has also been refreshed with contemporary waterfall-inspired fixtures, adding a spa-like touch to the home. A newly equipped laundry room with brand-new appliances adds convenience and efficiency to your daily routine. The finished basement provides additional entertainment space complete with a built-in bar, making it the perfect spot for hosting guests, game nights, or relaxing evenings at home. Outside, you'll find a detached 2-car garage and a spacious backyard, ideal for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying your own private retreat. The beautifully landscaped lawn enhances the home's curb appeal and creates a welcoming first impression. Conveniently located in Maple Heights, this home offers quick access to the highway for an easy commute and is less than one mile from Southgate Shopping Plaza, placing shopping, dining, and everyday essentials just minutes away. With thoughtful renovations, modern upgrades, and a highly convenient location, this move-in-ready bungalow offers comfort, style, and practicality all in one place."
      },
